    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Logic gameplay with a twist</h2>Move that Box is a retro arcade top-down action-puzzle game based on logical thinking that also requires reflexes. The game draws handfuls of Sokoban. The player's task is simple - get from point A to point B by moving boxes and solving puzzles. Move, push, throw, melt, and even blow up items to reach the goal.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Arcade style story</h2>Love of your life has been captured by aliens! She's stranded somewhere inside their mothership! <br>You must find her! But be careful, as the ship is full of...weird boxes!<br>Put on an alien suit and push through levels!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Puzzle Style Gameplay - Mix of puzzles that require logical thinking, reflexes, and blowing up stuff!<br></li><li>Bomb System  - Bombs that explode destroying 'everything' within one square,<br></li><li>Boxes - various types that can be interacted with - wooden that can be pushed through, metal ones, moveble by bomb explosions, and many more.<br></li><li>Every world has it's unique gameplay style,<br></li><li>Music - Ansimuz<br></li><li>Multiple game modes - With &quot;Story Mode&quot; completed you can try yourself in time and steps challenges,<br></li><li>Collectibles  - You can unlock a special skins for your hero!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Art style</h2>Retro style game with a touch of modern pixel art.",
